{"word":"ἀποχωρίζω","slug":"ἀποχωρίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀποχωρίζω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀπό\">ἀπό</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:χωρίζω\">χωρίζω</a></el>] ‘interrupt a close relationship by setting apart’, of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> sense <b><i>separate</i> <a href='B:510 15:39'>Ac 15:39</a>,</b> here <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ aor.\">aor.</a> with active force (our <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ colloq.\">colloq.</a> usage ‘split up’ of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> ending a close association is applicable); of the sky, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <b><i>split</i> <a href='B:730 6:14'>Rv 6:14</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀποχωρέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀποψύχω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}